headline: Fifth Third Enters Alabama with Ambitious Growth Plan
summary: CINCINNATI, August 12, 2025--Today, Fifth Third (Nasdaq: FITB) expands its retail presence into Alabama, launching its first financial center in Huntsville and marking a bold new chapter in the Bank’s 167-year history. With this milestone, the super-regional expands its retail footprint to 12 states, reinforcing its position as a banking leader.
